Zatch tells Kiyo he wants to know what having a mother feels like and Kiyo tells him to look at his mother like his own mother. Zatch angered by this runs away. Kiyo searches for Zatch and runs into Tia who helps him. Kiyo's mother finds Zatch who tells her he is afraid to accept her as his mother since his feelings for his real mother might be lost. Kiyo's mother tells Zatch that there is no problem in having two mothers in his heart, since she thinks of Zatch as her own son. Zatch realizes this must be what having a mother feels like and cries while hugging her.\n| LineColor       = FCC\n}}\n{{Episode list/sublist\n| 1               = List of Zatch Bell! episodes (season 3)\n| EpisodeNumber   = 109\n| Title           = Duel in the Northern Country. Fated Rival. Umagon Frozen!!\n| TranslitTitle   = Kitaguni no kettou Shukumei no raibaru Umagon hyouketsu!!\n| NativeTitle     = \u5317\u56fd\u306e\u6c7a\u95d8 \u5bbf\u547d\u306e\u30e9\u30a4\u30d0\u30eb \u30a6\u30de\u30b4\u30f3\u6c37\u7d50!!\n| NativeTitleLangCode = ja \n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2005|5|29}}\n| AltDate         = -\n| ShortSummary    = Sunbeam is told that he must go to [[Hokkaid\u014d]] for a week of training. He leaves his Mamodo [[Ponygon]] with Kiyo and Zatch. Zatch seeing how badly Ponygon wanted to go with Sunbeam helps Ponygon sneak aboard a plane. Zatch tells Ponygon to promise to return safely. After a week, Sunbeam prepares to buy some souvenirs before returning home but meets Ponygon on a ranch. They decide go to sight seeing around Hokkaid\u014d. Sunbeam learns from a waitress that the weather has been colder than usual and that there is still snow in the mountains. Sunbeam and Ponygon investigate and are attacked by the Mamodo pair [[List of Zatch Bell! characters#Cardio and Souza|Cardio and Souza]]. The pair calls Ponygon weak for having allies and proceeds the battle. The match is even until Souza uses a spell \"Dogikor Gidoruk\" that gives Cardio an upgrade to his armor and the abi